---
// EmilySystemBanner.astro - Баннер системы Эмили в 8-bit стиле
---

<section class="emily-banner">
	<div class="emily-banner__badge">LAB REPORT</div>
	<h2 class="emily-banner__title">EMILY COMPUTER: SYSTEM INITIALIZED</h2>
	<p class="emily-banner__text">
		Эмили запускает новый эксперимент. Поток данных усиливается, уровень шума растёт, 
		а Лаборатория адаптируется в реальном времени.
	</p>
	<div class="emily-banner__stats">
		<div class="stat-item">
			<span class="stat-label">STATUS:</span>
			<span class="stat-value">ONLINE</span>
		</div>
		<div class="stat-item">
			<span class="stat-label">EXPERIMENTS:</span>
			<span class="stat-value">ACTIVE</span>
		</div>
		<div class="stat-item">
			<span class="stat-label">DATA FLOW:</span>
			<span class="stat-value">OPTIMAL</span>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>

<style>
	.emily-banner {
		border: 4px solid var(--8bit-yellow);
		background: var(--8bit-black);
		padding: 20px;
		margin-bottom: 30px;
		position: relative;
		box-shadow: 0 0 20px var(--8bit-yellow);
		transition: all 0.05s linear;
	}

	.emily-banner:hover {
		box-shadow: 0 0 40px var(--8bit-yellow);
	}

	.emily-banner__badge {
		display: inline-block;
		padding: 8px 16px;
		border: 4px solid var(--8bit-yellow);
		background: var(--8bit-black);
		font-size: 0.75rem;
		color: var(--8bit-yellow);
		margin-bottom: 16px;
		text-transform: uppercase;
		letter-spacing: 2px;
		text-shadow: 3px 3px 0px #000000;
		box-shadow: 0 0 15px var(--8bit-yellow);
		transition: all 0.05s linear;
	}

	.emily-banner__badge:hover {
		box-shadow: 0 0 30px var(--8bit-yellow);
	}

	.emily-banner__title {
		font-size: 1.125rem;
		color: var(--8bit-lime);
		margin-bottom: 16px;
		line-height: 1.6;
		text-shadow: 3px 3px 0px #000000;
		font-family: var(--8bit-font) !important;
	}

	.emily-banner__text {
		font-size: 0.75rem;
		color: var(--8bit-white);
		line-height: 2;
		margin-bottom: 20px;
		opacity: 0.9;
		font-family: var(--8bit-font) !important;
		text-shadow: 1px 1px 0px #000000;
	}

	.emily-banner__stats {
		display: flex;
		gap: 24px;
		flex-wrap: wrap;
		padding-top: 20px;
		border-top: 4px solid var(--8bit-cyan);
	}

	.stat-item {
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		gap: 8px;
		padding: 8px;
		border: 4px solid var(--8bit-cyan);
		background: var(--8bit-black);
		box-shadow: 0 0 10px var(--8bit-cyan);
		transition: all 0.05s linear;
	}

	.stat-item:hover {
		box-shadow: 0 0 25px var(--8bit-cyan);
	}

	.stat-label {
		font-size: 0.625rem;
		color: var(--8bit-cyan);
		opacity: 0.9;
		text-transform: uppercase;
		text-shadow: 2px 2px 0px #000000;
		font-family: var(--8bit-font) !important;
	}

	.stat-value {
		font-size: 0.75rem;
		color: var(--8bit-lime);
		font-weight: normal;
		text-shadow: 3px 3px 0px #000000;
		font-family: var(--8bit-font) !important;
	}

	@media (max-width: 768px) {
		.emily-banner {
			padding: 16px;
		}

		.emily-banner__title {
			font-size: 0.875rem;
		}

		.emily-banner__text {
			font-size: 0.625rem;
		}

		.emily-banner__stats {
			flex-direction: column;
			gap: 12px;
		}

		.stat-item {
			padding: 6px;
		}
	}
</style>
